A mahogany toy box can be built in the Toy box space of the Costume Room in a player-owned house. It requires 86 Construction to build and when built, it gives 280 experience. The player must have a hammer and a saw in their inventory to build it.

It can be used to store toys and other holiday items, usually obtained through seasonal events.
